topic.title: Popularizing Zeronet
topic.body:
I love zeronet. I think it is a great idea with fluid implementation.


That being said, some of these websites are dusty as fuck. Some of the channels on here are pretty dead too.

How can we increase the active userbase and minimize the decrease in post quality?

The easy answer would  be to contribute good and unique content on zeronet only and to advertise only in places that you respect and frequent.

Any ideas? I wish zero was more active
